Correct Way to Use: Ground yourself while building computer, or working on sensitive electronics to prevent static charge build-up. Clean your hands and keep them dry, wear the grounding strap with the metal part touching your skin. Attach the metal clip to one of the grounding nodes on an anti static mat or a grounded metal surface. You're now ready to repair

Premium Quality & Warranty: STREBITO antistatic wrist straps have passed through resistance value(1M Ohms) test to properly protect against electrostatic discharge.
